            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>soured cream </strong>and <strong>chipotle paste</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to a small bowl with<strong> half</strong> your <strong>white wine vinegar </strong>(save the rest for later!) and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>creamy chipotle dressing</strong></p><p>Drain your <strong>sweetcorn</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1684835970918-x200.jpg",
