            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>smashed avocado </strong>and the <strong>diced tomato</strong> in a bowl with the <strong>chopped coriander</strong>, the <strong>remaining white wine vinegar</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up - this is your <strong>guacamole</strong></p>",
